query: SELECT pc.id, pc.parentUserId, pc.studentId, pc.relationship, u.name as parentName, s.displayName as studentName FROM parentChildren pc LEFT JOIN users u ON pc.parentUserId = u.id LEFT JOIN students s ON pc.studentId = s.id LIMIT 10
